            "title": "Comparing Things ⚖️",
            "content": "To act on different situations, we first need to **compare** values.\n\nWe ask questions like:\n* Is A bigger than B?\n* Does X equal Y?\n\nThe answer is always a **Boolean** (true or false)."
        },
